      "text": "- Model\n    - Disaster\n    - Location\n    - Users\n    - ....\n\n- Controller\n    - Disaster Controller\n    - Assignment Controller\n    - ....\n\n- Service\n    - Disaster Service\n    - Assignment Service\n    - Notification Service\n    -....\n\n- Repository\n    - Disaster Repo\n    - Users Repo\n    - ....\n\n- Cron Jobs\n    - EarthQuekes Service\n    - Flood Service\n    - .....\n\n- Notifications\n    - RabbitMQ service\n    - Websocket Manager",
