      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777989710949,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Endpoints:\n    Auth:\n        - POST /api/auth/login\n        - POST /api/auth/register\n\n    Assignment:\n        - GET /api/assignments\n        - GET /api/assignments/{assignment_id}\n        - GET /api/assignments?assigned_to\n        - GET /api/assignments?assigned_by    \n        - POST /api/assignments\n\n    Disaster:\n        - GET /api/disasters/nearby\n        - POST /api/disasters\n        - GET  /api/disasters\n        - GET  /api/disasters/{id}\n        - PUT  /api/disasters/{id}\n        - DELETE /api/disasters/{id} \n\n    User:\n        - [Admin] PATCH /api/users/{user_id}/activate\n        - [Admin] PATCH /api/users/{user_id}/deactivate\n        - [Coordinator] \n\n    Resource:\n        - POST /api/resources\n        - GET /api/resources\n        - GET /api/resources/{resource_id}\n        - PATCH /api/resources/{resource_id}/status\n\n    Notification:\n        - GET /api/notifications\n        - GET /api/notifications/{notification_id}\n        - PATCH /api/notifications/{notification_id}/read\n\n    Volunteer Profile:\n        - PATCH /api/volunteers/status   -> Get user id from JWT\n        - GET  /api/volunteers/available \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Endpoints:\n    Auth:\n        - POST /api/auth/login\n        - POST /api/auth/register\n\n    Assignment:\n        - GET /api/assignments\n        - GET /api/assignments/{assignment_id}\n        - GET /api/assignments?assigned_to\n        - GET /api/assignments?assigned_by    \n        - POST /api/assignments\n\n    Disaster:\n        - GET /api/disasters/nearby\n        - POST /api/disasters\n        - GET  /api/disasters\n        - GET  /api/disasters/{id}\n        - PUT  /api/disasters/{id}\n        - DELETE /api/disasters/{id} \n\n    User:\n        - [Admin] PATCH /api/users/{user_id}/activate\n        - [Admin] PATCH /api/users/{user_id}/deactivate\n        - [Coordinator] \n\n    Resource:\n        - POST /api/resources\n        - GET /api/resources\n        - GET /api/resources/{resource_id}\n        - PATCH /api/resources/{resource_id}/status\n\n    Notification:\n        - GET /api/notifications\n        - GET /api/notifications/{notification_id}\n        - PATCH /api/notifications/{notification_id}/read\n\n    Volunteer Profile:\n        - PATCH /api/volunteers/status   -> Get user id from JWT\n        - GET  /api/volunteers/available \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
